-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">Average rating across every verified listing in Franklin. Reflects cleanliness, amenities, and community feedback.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card \"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Verified reviews</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">6,064</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">Community reviews informing our quality score. Tap any park card below to see highlights.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card \"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Park availability</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">36</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">Total verified listings currently live for Franklin. Fresh listings added weekly.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card \"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Indoor options</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">—</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">Indoor options are being scouted—submit a favorite and we will feature it.</p></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenities-row\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenities-header\"><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db\">Most common amenities</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db\">What people are looking for and finding in <!-- -->Franklin<!-- -->.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenities-chips\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenity-chip\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-percentage\">100<!-- -->%</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-label\">Onsite services</span></span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenity-chip\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-percentage\">100<!-- -->%</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-label\">Indoor facilities</span></span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db amenity-chip\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-percentage\">100<!-- -->%</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chip-label\">Profession