ong collars</li><li>Monitor play styles and intervene early</li><li>Share shaded space and refill water when you&#x27;re done</li></ul></article></div></div></section><section id=\"owner-cta\" class=\"owner-cta-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Partner with us</span><h2>Feature your Franklin dog park</h2><p>Upgrade to a featured listing, share live availability, or pitch a new indoor concept. Our team drives qualified local pet parents every week.</p><div class=\"hero-cta-row\" style=\"margin-top:24px\"><a class=\"hero-cta primary\" href=\"/list-your-park\">List a property</a><a class=\"hero-cta ghost\" href=\"/contact\">Contact the team</a></div></div></section><section id=\"park-directory\" class=\"park-directory-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">City directory</span><h2>All dog parks in <!-- -->Franklin</h2><p>Filter-ready cards with ratings, amenities, and quick actions. Use the chips to jump between sections.</p></div><div class=\"category-chip-row\"><button type=\"button\">Dog Park</button></div><div id=\"dog-park-parks\" class=\"directory-category\"><div class=\"directory-header\"><div><h3>Dog Park<!-- -->s<!-- --> in <!-- -->Franklin</h3><p>36<!-- --> locations ·<!-- --> <!-- -->4.4<!-- --> <!-- -->average rating</p></div><span class=\"directory-count\">36</span></div><div class=\"directory-grid\"><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/4-the-love-of-paws\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">4 the love of Paws</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">Closed</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Opens tomorrow at 7:00 AM</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Franklin<!-- -->, <!-- -->TN</span></div><div class=\"park-p