s praise from pet owners. This facility specializes in Pet care and Professional services. For more information, call (615) 662-6628. Visit their website at http://thefarmatnatcheztrace.com/day-care/woof-club/ to learn more about their services and pricing.\",\"slug\":\"woof-club\",\"address\":\"9479 Hwy 96\",\"street\":\"9479 Hwy 96\",\"city\":\"Franklin\",\"state\":\"TN\",\"zipCode\":\"37064\",\"full_address\":\"9479 Hwy 96, Franklin, TN 37064, USA\",\"latitude\":35.9994134,\"longitude\":-87.0210717,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJ1XB7juOFZIgRaSchLMr6boU\",\"phone\":\"(615) 662-6628\",\"website\":\"http://thefarmatnatcheztrace.com/day-care/woof-club/\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":5,\"reviewCount\":1,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"7:00 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"7:00 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"7:00 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"7:00 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"7:00 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"10:00 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"10:00 AM – 6:00 PM\"},\"amenities\":{\"Onsite services\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,\"Professional staff\":true,\"Climate controlled\":true,\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\":false,\"Parking available\":true,\"Easy access\":true},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"}],\"cityName\":\"Franklin\",\"insightCards\":\"$undefined\",\"topAmenities\":[{\"key\":\"Onsite services\",\"label\":\"Onsite services\",\"count\":36,\"share\":100},{\"key\":\"Indoor facilities\",\"label\":\"Indoor facilities\",\"count\":36,\"share\":100},{\"key\":\"Professional staff\",\"label\":\"Professional staff\",\"count\":36,\"share\":100},{\"key\":\"Climate controlled\",\"label\":\"Climate controlled\",\"count\":36,\"share\":100},{\"key\":\"Parking available\",\"label\":\"Parking available\",\"count\":36,\"share\":100},{\"key\":\"Easy access\",\"label\":\"Easy access\"